data.description: Steep roof lines and storybook touches of a cottage style home, this three bedrooms house gives a warm welcome. On the main level enjoy hardwood floors and cozy up next to the wood burning fireplace in the living room & dine with guests in the formal dining room. Cook your favorite dish in the vintage style kitchen that mixes the past with the practicality of the present. The upper level features three bedroom & lower level has space for recreation. A fully fenced backyard with a screened patio, storage shed, mature trees & yard for games or gardens. Schedule a showing today.
